<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
    xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
    xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
    xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
    lang="en"
    metal:use-macro="context/main_template/macros/master"
    i18n:domain="mingjing.content">
<body>

<metal:row define-macro="cover-news">
<!-- news -->
<div id="index-news">
<div id="index-news-photo-b"><img src="${context/absolute_url}/@@images/whatsNew_bigImage/large" /></div>
<div id="index-news-box">
<div id="tai-index-news"><a href="${context/whatsNew_URI}" onmouseout="MM_swapImgRestore()"
                            onmouseover="MM_swapImage('Image9','','${prefix}images/tai-news-b.png',1)">
                            <img src="${prefix}images/tai-news.png" id="Image9" />
                        </a>
</div>
<div id="index-news-photo-s"><img src="${context/absolute_url}/@@images/whatsNew_smallImage/preview" /></div>
<div id="index-news-words">
<h4>${context/whatsNew_title}</h4>
<p><a href="${context/whatsNew_URI}" class="black-link">${context/whatsNew_text}</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- news end -->
</metal:row>


<metal:row define-macro="cover-more-feast-text">
<!-- music -->
<div id="index-music">
<div id="tai-index-music"><a href="#" onmouseout="MM_swapImgRestore()" onmouseover="MM_swapImage('Image18','','${prefix}images/tai-music-b.png',1)"><img src="${prefix}images/tai-music.png" id="Image18" /></a></div>
<a name="notice01" id="notice01"></a>
<div id="index-music-box">
  <div id="index-music-box01"><img src="${prefix}images/tai-music-ch.png" /></div>
<div id="index-music-box02">${context/moreFeast_text}</div>
<!-- item -->
<div id="index-music-box03">
<ul>
<li><section><a href="#notice" class="button" onmouseout="MM_swapImgRestore()" onmouseover="MM_swapImage('Image20','','${prefix}images/btn-music01-b.png',1)"><img src="${prefix}images/btn-music01.png" id="Image20" /></a></section></li>
<li><a href="content/musicman/musicman-list.html" onmouseout="MM_swapImgRestore()" onmouseover="MM_swapImage('Image21','','${prefix}images/btn-music02-b.png',1)"><img src="${prefix}images/btn-music02.png" id="Image21" /></a></li>
<li><a href="content/recommend/recommend-list.html" onmouseout="MM_swapImgRestore()" onmouseover="MM_swapImage('Image22','','${prefix}images/btn-music03-b.png',1)"><img src="${prefix}images/btn-music03.png" id="Image22" /></a></li>
<li><a href="content/links/links-01.html" onmouseout="MM_swapImgRestore()" onmouseover="MM_swapImage('Image23','','${prefix}images/btn-music04-b.png',1)"><img src="${prefix}images/btn-music04.png" id="Image23" /></a></li>
</ul>
</div>
<!-- item end -->
</div>
</div>
<!-- music end -->
</metal:row>


<metal:row define-macro="cover-about">
<div id="index-about">
<p>日前，由 flyingV 群眾募資平台所舉辦的「問一 Shot 之夜」音樂小聚圓滿結束！當天活動邀請到「相知國際」品牌與行銷部行銷總監江季剛、策略與企劃部創意總監沈彥呈、「Packer 派歌」版權經理張書珩、「大港開唱」宣傳公關總召呂岱芸、「激進工作室」負責人陳威仲、自由工作者耿璐及「flyingV」專案經理林乃禎，從自身經驗出發，擔任不同面向的給問關主，用輕鬆的「喝一杯 Shot，答一個問」方式為各獨立音樂人、樂團解答心中盤旋許久的疑問。
    <a href="content/about/about-01.html" onmouseout="MM_swapImgRestore()" onmouseover="MM_swapImage('Image24','','${prefix}images/btn-more-b.png',1)">
        <img src="${prefix}images/btn-more.png" id="Image24" hspace="15" align="center" />
    </a>
</p>
<div id="index-btn-3d">
    <a href="content/3d-lab/lab-01.html" onmouseout="MM_swapImgRestore()" onmouseover="MM_swapImage('Image25','','${prefix}images/btn-3d-b.png',1)">
        <img src="${prefix}images/btn-3d.png" id="Image25" />
    </a>
</div>
</div>
</metal:row>

<metal:row define-macro="big-image">
<div id="ad-f" tal:condition="python:getattr(context, 'bigImage_1', False) or getattr(context, 'bigImage_2', False)">
<!-- InstanceBeginEditable name="ad" -->
<div style="max-height:958px; overflow:hidden">
    <img tal:condition="python:getattr(context, 'bigImage_1', False)"
         tal:attributes="src string:${context/absolute_url}/@@images/bigImage_1/bigImage" />
</div>
<div style="max-height:958px; overflow:hidden">
<img tal:condition="python:getattr(context, 'bigImage_2', False)"
     tal:attributes="src string:${context/absolute_url}/@@images/bigImage_2/bigImage" />
</div>
<!-- InstanceEndEditable -->
</div>
</metal:row>

</body>
</html>


